###############################
# Specify routing options when
# running hogwash in inline mode
#
# Currently supported routing options:
#  SBridge(interface1, interface2)
#    Just pass all the packets.
#  MacFilter(interface, interface, ...)
#    SBridge with network flood protection
#    Supports more than 2 interfaces.
#    Use this if your switches crash.
#  Broadcast()
#    Turn on specific support for 
#    ethernet broadcast packets.
#    Most of the time you won't
#    need this.
#  SIP(INTERFACE IPLIST)
#    Route the given IPs out the
#    given interface.
#  DIP(INTERFACE IPLIST)
#    Route the given IPs out the
#    given interface.
###############################

<routing>
